ABSTRACT
Methods and apparatus are provided for a network to control
a power of transmissions from a User Equipment (UE) on a
first Cell Group (CG) or on a second CG depending on a
communication delay between the two CGs. Methods and
apparatus are also provided for a UE configured with a first
CG and a second CG in Carrier Aggregation (CA) operation
to determine whether or not to transmit a channel conveying
control information when the UE needs to reduce a respec-
tive nominal transmission power. Methods and apparatus are
additionally provided for a network to transmit and for a UE
to receive a Transmission Power Control (TPC) command
for transmission on a cell of a first CG or on a cell of a
second CG.
